{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "自幽暗归来者 第13章 4-1 被他人所需要",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": [
            "剧情概要"
        ],
        "content": [
            "在昔日的王都，巴尔库斯找到了\\n即将启程前往香榭利亚的利弗。\\n巴尔库斯虽然已看穿利弗打算离开王都、\\n与王子一行人会合的心思，但因通过交谈\\n感受到了利弗坚定的信念，便放走了他。"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "尤蒂尔一行人\\n在黎布湖的同时，王都中……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120008_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国兵",
            "context": "巴尔库斯将军！\\n王都内已经巡逻完毕。\\n没有发现任何异常。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_05_0001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100016_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴尔库斯",
            "context": "辛苦了。退下吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_05_0002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120008_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国兵",
            "context": "是！不过，真是可惜了这王都的风景……\\n没想到这种市区也要建起屏障……\\n可恶……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_05_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100016_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴尔库斯",
            "context": "你这……话里有话啊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_05_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120008_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国兵",
            "context": "塞西娅大人……为什么要\\n不断实施这种暴行呢？甚至不惜\\n借用崇拜魔神的远古国家之名……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_05_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100016_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴尔库斯",
            "context": "你不喜欢狄涅尔这个名字？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_05_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120008_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国兵",
            "context": "当然了。这简直就像是\\n连我们也崇拜着魔神一样。\\n为什么非要遵从魔神呢！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_05_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120008_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国兵",
            "context": "与其继续忍受这种屈辱，\\n我们不如也像第七王子那样……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_05_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100016_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴尔库斯",
            "context": "这是你的感想，\\n还是对我的谏言？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_05_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120008_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国兵",
            "context": "怎、怎么会是谏言……\\n绝对不是！\\n只是属下的感想而已！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_05_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100016_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴尔库斯",
            "context": "那你就管好自己的嘴。\\n归队吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_05_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120008_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国兵",
            "context": "是！非常抱歉……\\n那属下就先行告退！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_05_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100016_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴尔库斯",
            "context": "为什么要遵从魔神吗……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_05_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100016_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴尔库斯",
            "context": "问了我同样问题的那个男人，\\n现在正在做什么呢……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_05_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100016_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "昔日的王都",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100016_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴尔库斯",
            "context": "利弗，你要去哪里？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_05_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "巴尔库斯大人。\\n我接到谢斯大人的紧急号令，\\n正要前往香榭利亚。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_05_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100016_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴尔库斯",
            "context": "不光是你一个人，\\n还要带上整个白燕骑士团吗。\\n这事真蹊跷啊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_05_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "这都是谢斯大人的命令。\\n任务结束后会立即返回王都。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_05_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100016_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴尔库斯",
            "context": "别演了……\\n你们不会再回王都了吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_05_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100016_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴尔库斯",
            "context": "你会率领着骑士团\\n顺势背叛狄涅尔帝国。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_05_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100016_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴尔库斯",
            "context": "最后会前往圣城， \\n与尤蒂尔汇合——\\n在我看来会是这样。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_05_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "看来什么事\\n都瞒不过巴尔库斯大人……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_05_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100016_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴尔库斯",
            "context": "果然这就是你内心所想。\\n那么……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_05_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100016_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴尔库斯",
            "context": "从这一刻起，\\n你就是帝国的叛徒。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_05_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "巴尔库斯大人……\\n我不打算与您动武。\\n请收回您的武器。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_05_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100016_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴尔库斯",
            "context": "你觉得我会在扬言要造反之人\\n面前收回我的剑吗？\\n你也已经做好觉悟了吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_05_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "我早已做好了觉悟。\\n但是，巴尔库斯大人\\n是不会这么做的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_05_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100016_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴尔库斯",
            "context": "你这个男人\\n还真是刚正不阿……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_05_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100016_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴尔库斯",
            "context": "你快离开王都吧……\\n如果皇帝陛下下了讨伐令，\\n就不会像现在这样和平收场了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_05_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "巴尔库斯大人……\\n为什么您要遵从魔神，\\n留在王都呢？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_05_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "在魔神扭曲的庇护下，\\n这个国家不会迎来真正的和平。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_05_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "我想巴尔库斯大人\\n不会不懂这个道理。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_05_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100016_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴尔库斯",
            "context": "我是以武侍国之人，\\n对我来说认谁为将不是问题。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_05_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100016_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴尔库斯",
            "context": "我的使命就是不断铲除\\n当下威胁民众的敌人。\\n仅此而已……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_05_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "这想法很符合\\n巴尔库斯大人的作风。\\n您果然是具备武将品行之人。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_05_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "回想我们二人\\n一起练剑的那些日子，\\n我总是会被您强大的气场所压制。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_05_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "您付出极大努力不断进行锻炼，\\n为拥有精湛武艺而努力的身影，\\n至今还映在我的脑海里。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_05_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100016_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴尔库斯",
            "context": "兄长和姐姐都是充满才气的人。\\n我一直都担心他们的才气\\n会成为分裂国家的主要原因。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_05_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "巴尔库斯大人……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_05_0039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100016_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴尔库斯",
            "context": "我为了不输给兄长和姐姐，\\n才不断锻炼自己。但是，\\n尤蒂尔竟然……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_05_0040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100016_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴尔库斯",
            "context": "一个人的才能无法预测。\\n我本以为他虽然待人宽厚，\\n但意志力很薄弱，没想到……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_05_0041",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100016_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴尔库斯",
            "context": "利弗，在你眼里，\\n尤蒂尔\\n是一个什么样的人？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_05_0042",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "殿下，就像是一道光。\\n虽然现在还很微弱渺小，\\n却为了指引我们而散发着光芒。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_05_0043",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100016_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴尔库斯",
            "context": "这么看好他吗。既然如此，\\n你就尽管遵从自己的想法\\n去他那里吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_05_0044",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100016_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴尔库斯",
            "context": "我会在这里率领军队保卫国家。\\n即使被蔑视为魔神的爪牙\\n也在所不惜。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_05_0045",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "这就是巴尔库斯大人\\n找到的答案啊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_05_0046",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100016_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴尔库斯",
            "context": "很奇怪吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_05_0047",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "不……\\n您的觉悟很伟大。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_05_0048",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "只要我们走在彼此坚信的路上，\\n终有一天会再次相遇。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_05_0049",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100016_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴尔库斯",
            "context": "如果你加入了尤蒂尔军，\\n下次再见面的时候\\n我们也许就是敌人了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_05_0050",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100016_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴尔库斯",
            "context": "战场上我不会手下留情，\\n一定会拼尽全力打败你。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_05_0051",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "即使遇到那种情况，\\n我也做好了作为一名骑士\\n与巴尔库斯大人正面交锋的觉悟。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_05_0052",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "那么，就此别过。\\n巴尔库斯大人，请珍重……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_05_0053",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100016_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴尔库斯",
            "context": "……\\n等一下，利弗。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_05_0054",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "是……您请讲。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_05_0055",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100016_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴尔库斯",
            "context": "在我打败你之前……\\n你不能死。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_05_0056",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "遵命，巴尔库斯大人。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_05_0057",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100016_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴尔库斯",
            "context": "（新阿尔贝里亚王国与狄涅尔帝国\\n一决胜负之日就要到来了吗……）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_05_0058",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100016_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴尔库斯",
            "context": "（我会作为帝国将领贯彻自己的信念。\\n就算被人嘲笑顽固\\n或是狭隘也无所谓。）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_05_0059",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120008_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国兵",
            "context": "巴尔库斯将军！\\n属下有事禀报！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_05_0060",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100016_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴尔库斯",
            "context": "出什么事了？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_05_0061",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120008_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国兵",
            "context": "边境部队来报，有可疑人群\\n已南下至边境附近。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_05_0062",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100016_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴尔库斯",
            "context": "是北方的哪个国家\\n派出的军队吗。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_05_0063",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120008_01"
